'''康尼島-斯提威爾大道車站'''（{{lang-en|Coney Island–Stillwell Avenue station}}），又稱「康尼島總站」（{{lang|en|Coney Island Terminal}}），部分列車以「康尼島」或「斯提威爾大道」顯示站名，是位於[[美國|美國]][[紐約市|紐約市]][[布魯克林|布魯克林]][[康尼島|康尼島]]的[[紐約地鐵|紐約地鐵]][[總站|總站]]，同時是[[紐約地鐵D線|D線]]、[[紐約地鐵F線|F線]]、[[紐約地鐵N線|N線]]及[[紐約地鐵Q線|Q線]]列車的總站。車站的大型設施在1919年興建，當時以康尼島作為[[紐約都會區|紐約都會區]]的夏季渡假區設計，所有布魯克林南面的鐵路都漏斗型方式前往此地區。此站是世界上最大的高架交通總站之一。

康尼島-斯提威爾大道車站設有四個[[島式月台|島式月台]]和四條軌道，列車分別從南北兩面進站。此站位於康尼島斯提威爾大道和衝浪大道交界，也是舊西城總站所在地。地理上也是紐約地鐵最南端的總站。

== 歷史 ==
=== 起源 ===
康尼島的鐵路交通自1864年開始營運，{{link-en|西城線 (布魯克林地面)|West End Line (Brooklyn surface)|布魯克林、巴斯及康尼島鐵路}}是第一條前往康尼島{{link-en|蒸汽鐵路|steam railroad}}。該線由現時是[[日落公園_(布魯克林)|日落公園]]的第五大道及36街開始運行<ref name=":3">{{Cite web|url=http://www.arrts-arrchives.com/whats_new.html|title=WEST END LINE|last=Huneke|first=Arthur John|date=|website=www.arrts-arrchives.com|publisher=|access-date=2016-08-15|archive-date=2021-08-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210830092322/http://arrts-arrchives.com/whats_new.html}}</ref>到西城總站，現時康尼島總站的位置<ref name=":4">{{Cite web|url=http://forgotten-ny.com/2002/08/alls-well-thats-stillwell-a-trip-to-the-soon-demolished-stillwell-avenue-terminal-going-in-style-on-1925-vintage-d-type-triplexes/|title=OLD STILLWELL AVE. TERMINAL — Forgotten New York|last=Walsh|first=Kevin|date=August 2002|website=forgotten-ny.com|publisher=[[Forgotten_NY|Forgotten NY]]|access-date=2016-08-15|archive-date=2020-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200812113615/https://forgotten-ny.com/2002/08/alls-well-thats-stillwell-a-trip-to-the-soon-demolished-stillwell-avenue-terminal-going-in-style-on-1925-vintage-d-type-triplexes/}}</ref>，沿現時西城線路線行走<ref name=":3" /><ref name=":6">{{Cite web|url=http://thethirdrail.net./0305/stillwell1.html|title=The New BMT Coney Island Terminal|last=Matus|first=Paul|date=May 2003|website=thethirdrail.net|publisher=|page=1|access-date=2016-08-15|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161017050912/http://thethirdrail.net/0305/stillwell1.html|archivedate=2016-10-17}}</ref>。鄰近的[[紐約地鐵車廠#卡爾弗車廠|卡爾弗車廠]]，沿[[大西洋|大西洋]]海岸近現時[[西八街-紐約水族館車站|西八街]]車站，服務[[BMT布萊頓線|布魯克林、夫拉特布殊及康尼島鐵路]]（現時布萊頓線）及{{link-en|卡爾弗線 (地面)|Culver Line (surface)|展望公園及康尼島鐵路}}（現時卡爾弗線）<ref name=":4" /><ref name=":7">{{Cite web|url=http://thethirdrail.net./0305/stillwell2.html|title=The New BMT Coney Island Terminal|last=Matus|first=Paul|date=May 2003|website=thethirdrail.net|publisher=|page=2|access-date=2016-08-15|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130629030844/http://thethirdrail.net/0305/stillwell2.html|archivedate=2013-06-29}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.arrts-arrchives.com/cibrtterm.html|title=Coney Island CULVER Terminal|last=Huneke|first=Arthur John|date=|website=www.arrts-arrchives.com|publisher=|access-date=2016-08-15|archive-date=2021-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211210054758/http://arrts-arrchives.com/cibrtterm.html}}</ref><ref name="StreetRR-CulverTerm-Jun1904">{{cite journal|title=An Improved Terminal For Handling the Heavy Coney Island Crowds–Brooklyn Rapid Transit Company|journal=Street Railway Journal|date=1904-06-11|volume=23|issue=24|pages=884–888|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=EqNPAQAAMAAJ&pg=PA880-IA2|accessdate=2016-09-04|publisher=[[McGraw_Publishing_Company|McGraw Publishing Company]]}}
* {{cite news|title=The Brooklyn Rapid Transit's New Culver Terminal|url=https://www.newspapers.com/image/53413932/?terms=%22culver%27s%2Bdepot%22|accessdate=2016-09-02|work=[[Brooklyn_Daily_Eagle|Brooklyn Daily Eagle]]|via=[[Newspapers.com|Newspapers.com]]|date=1904-05-15|page=8|archive-date=2020-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200919194810/https://www.newspapers.com/image/53413932/?terms=%22culver%27s%2Bdepot%22}}
* {{cite journal|title=The Rehabilitation of the Brooklyn Rapid Transit Company|journal=[[Railroad_Gazette|Railroad Gazette]]|date=1907-05-17|volume=42|issue=20|pages=670–673|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=-I1MAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA670|accessdate=2016-09-02}}
* {{cite web |last=Feinman |first=Mark S. |title=www.nycsubway.org: Early Rapid Transit in Brooklyn, 1878–1913 |website=www.nycsubway.org |date=2001-02-17 |url=http://www.nycsubway.org/wiki/Early_Rapid_Transit_in_Brooklyn,_1878-1913 |accessdate=2015-11-12 |archive-date=2022-05-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220504004855/https://www.nycsubway.org/wiki/Early_Rapid_Transit_in_Brooklyn,_1878-1913 }}</ref>。其他鐵路交通包括{{link-en|曼哈頓海灘支線|Manhattan Beach Branch|曼哈頓海灘鐵路}}、[[BMT海灘線|海灘鐵路]]、{{link-en|康尼島及布魯克林鐵路|Coney Island and Brooklyn Railroad}}及經[[長島鐵路|長島鐵路]]前往[[長島市|長島市]]<ref name=":8">{{Cite web|url=http://www.westland.net/coneyisland/articles/transportation.htm|title=Coney Island History -Development of Rail and Steamboat Lines to the resort|first=Jeffrey|last=Stanton|date=1998-06-02|website=www.westland.net|publisher=Westland|access-date=2016-08-15|archive-date=2021-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210419100841/https://www.westland.net/coneyisland/articles/transportation.htm}}</ref><ref name=":6" />。

這些鐵路並不互相連接，導致島內有許多支線出現<ref name=":7" />。然而，布萊頓、卡爾弗、海灘及西城鐵路在1890年代末由{{link-en|布魯克林捷運公司|Brooklyn Rapid Transit Company}}收購，而1913年簽署的{{link-en|雙重合約|Dual Contracts}}容許在[[紐約市|紐約市]]內興建更多地鐵路線。布魯克林在15年之前併入紐約市一部分<ref name="StreetRR-CulverTerm-Jun1904"/><ref name=":9">{{Cite web|url=http://thethirdrail.net./0305/stillwell4.html|title=The New BMT Coney Island Terminal|last=Matus|first=Paul|date=May 2003|website=thethirdrail.net|publisher=|page=4|access-date=2016-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303172251/http://thethirdrail.net/0305/stillwell4.html|archive-date=2016-03-03|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

=== 新西城總站 ===
