1910年代末重新在高架結構上興建了「新西城總站」（逐步成為「康尼島總站」）。新總站統一了多數舊蒸汽鐵路線在康尼島的總站<ref name=":19">{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=OACbAwAAQBAJ&pg=PA87&lpg=PA87|title=Coney Island|last=Hoffman|first=Laura J.|date=2014-06-09|publisher=Arcadia Publishing|year=|isbn=9781467121316|location=|pages=87|language=en}}</ref>，只有長島鐵路控制的{{link-en|紐約及曼哈頓海灘鐵路|New York and Manhattan Beach Railway}}例外<ref name=":9" />。這個新總站每日可處理數十萬人流<ref name=":19" />。這個計劃還將布萊頓線和卡爾弗線由地面配置移到高架結構上，設有四個月台和八條軌道<ref name=":9" />。

BRT營運的海灘線，在1917年9月5日作為總站開放<ref name=":5">{{Cite news|url=http://timesmachine.nytimes.com/timesmachine/1917/09/05/96265495.html?pageNumber=8|title=OPEN FIRST SECTION OF BROADWAY LINE; Train Carrying 1,000 Passengers Runs from Fourteenth Street to Coney Island.REGULAR SERVICE BEGINSNew Road Is Expected to Relieve Old System of 15,000 PersonsDaily in Rush Hours. Service Commissioners Jubliant. Schedule Not Fully Arranged.|last=|first=|date=1917-09-05|work=|newspaper=The New York Times|issn=0362-4331|access-date=2016-08-15|via=}}</ref>，而BRT西城線同樣在1918年12月23日通車<ref name=":8" /><ref name=":9" />。總站在1919年5月29日新的布萊頓線開放時正式開放<ref name=":8" /><ref name=":9" /><ref name=":19" /><ref name=":14">{{Cite web|url=http://www.mta.info/news/2014/05/20/stillwell-terminal-remains-sparkling-jewel-decade-after-full-rehabilitation|title=Stillwell Terminal Remains a Sparkling Jewel a Decade after Full Rehabilitation|last=|first=|date=2014-05-20|website=www.mta.info|publisher=[[Metropolitan_Transportation_Authority|Metropolitan Transportation Authority]]|access-date=2016-08-15|archive-date=2021-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211201101739/https://www.mta.info/news/2014/05/20/stillwell-terminal-remains-sparkling-jewel-decade-after-full-rehabilitation}}</ref>。卡爾弗線1920年5月1日啟用後，總站終於全部完工 <ref name=":8" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://forgotten-ny.com/2001/02/the-new-york-stubways-remnants-of-long-gone-elevated-lines/|title=THE NEW YORK STUBWAYS. Remnants of long-gone elevated lines|last=Walsh|first=Kevin|date=February 2001|website=forgotten-ny.com|publisher=[[Forgotten_New_York|Forgotten New York]]|access-date=2016-08-15|archive-date=2021-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211107215554/https://forgotten-ny.com/2001/02/the-new-york-stubways-remnants-of-long-gone-elevated-lines/}}</ref><ref name=":15">{{Cite news|url=https://select.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=FB0C17FF3B5511738DDDA10A94DC405B808EF1D3|title=CONEY FARE CUT SATURDAY.; One Nickel to Take Passenger Over Lines of the B.R.T.|date=1920-04-28|newspaper=The New York Times|issn=0362-4331|access-date=2016-08-15|archive-date=2012-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121020035302/http://select.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=FB0C17FF3B5511738DDDA10A94DC405B808EF1D3}}</ref><ref name=":16">{{Cite news|url=https://select.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=F30611F83555157A93C3A9178ED85F448285F9|title=5-CENT FARE TO CONEY.; Change Is Effective Today on B.R. T. Elevated and Subway Lines.|date=1920-05-01|newspaper=The New York Times|issn=0362-4331|access-date=2016-08-15|archive-date=2012-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121020035325/http://select.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=F30611F83555157A93C3A9178ED85F448285F9|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

作為卡爾弗線延伸線的結果，BRT的車費由10美仙減至5美仙<ref name=":15" /><ref name=":16" />，而康尼島成為更能負擔的渡假地區。1923年，這些路線轉交BRT的繼承公司[[布魯克林-曼哈頓運輸股份有限公司|布魯克林-曼哈頓運輸股份有限公司]]（BMT）<ref name=":8" />。新車站的乘客一度獲得官方保證尖峰時間每三分鐘開行一班列車，但很快就證實無法實行。1923年，一名《{{link-en|布魯克林時報-聯合報|Brooklyn Times-Union|布魯克林標準聯合報}}》記者觀察到尖峰時段列車在海灘線班次是8分鐘，而西城線則是15分鐘，而尖峰時段沒有任何直接前往曼哈頓的列車，無論是布萊頓線或卡爾弗線<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://fultonhistory.com/highlighter/highlight-for-xml?uri=http%253A%252F%252Ffultonhistory.com%252FNewspaper%25252014%252FBrooklyn%252520NY%252520Standard%252520Union%252FBrooklyn%252520NY%252520Standard%252520Union%2525201923%252FBrooklyn%252520NY%252520Standard%252520Union%2525201923%252520-%2525200352.pdf&xml=http%253A%252F%252Ffultonhistory.com%252FdtSearch%252Fdtisapi6.dll%253Fcmd%253Dgetpdfhits%2526u%253Dffffffffe507bbb6%2526DocId%253D4653502%2526Index%253DZ%25253a%25255cIndex%252520U%25252dF%25252dP%2526HitCount%253D10%2526hits%253D3a%252B3b%252B3c%252Bda%252Bdb%252Bdc%252B1a2%252B1a3%252B1a4%252Bf04%252B%2526SearchForm%253D%25252fFulton%25255fNew%25255fform%25252ehtml%2526.pdf&openFirstHlPage=false|title=Weather Subdues Police of BRT|last=|first=|date=1923-01-18|website=fultonhistory.com|publisher=[[Brooklyn_Standard_Union|Brooklyn Standard Union]]|access-date=2016-08-15}}</ref>。

1929年，BMT宣佈為車站增加一個新入口。新入口將設有零售區，並會「定期檢查」<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.newspapers.com/image/59872613/?terms=new%2Bwest%2Bend%2Bterminal|title=New Entrance Planned For West End Terminal|last=|first=|date=1929-02-19|work=[[Brooklyn_Daily_Eagle|Brooklyn Daily Eagle]]|access-date=2016-08-15|via=[[newspapers.com|newspapers.com]]|archive-date=2020-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926191130/https://www.newspapers.com/image/59872613/?terms=new%2Bwest%2Bend%2Bterminal}}</ref>。1933年6月宣佈了新的布萊頓－富蘭克林平日列車服務。這列車將以快速的方式提供由[[富蘭克林大道車站_(BMT富蘭克林大道線)|富蘭克林大道]]前往康尼島的直接列車服務。卡爾弗高架鐵路列車將途經{{link-en|桑斯街車站 (BMT)|Sands Street (BMT station)|桑斯街}}或{{link-en|公園臺車站 (BMT)|Park Row (BMT station)|公園臺}}，視乎當日時間<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://query.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=9500E2DA1F3AE333A25756C2A9609C946294D6CF|title=NEW B.M.T. SERVICE.; Brighton-Franklin Trains to Coney Island to Run Weekdays.|date=1933-06-25|newspaper=The New York Times|issn=0362-4331|access-date=2016-08-16}}</ref>。

康尼島總站設有轉乘諾頓點街車前往{{link-en|海門 (布魯克林)|Sea Gate, Brooklyn|海門}}，途經高架天橋橫跨斯提威爾大道前往高架街車車站<ref name=":4" />。1948年街車服務終止，因為其餘另一條街車路線大致重疊（名為{{link-en|卡爾弗線 (地面)|Culver Line (surface)|麥當勞大道線}}）<ref name=":4" /><ref name="Forgotten New York 2012">{{cite web|url=http://forgotten-ny.com/1999/10/nortons-point-trolley-brooklyn/|title=NORTONS POINT TROLLEY, Brooklyn|date=2012-03-03|website=Forgotten New York|accessdate=2016-08-16|archive-date=2019-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191205200944/https://forgotten-ny.com/1999/10/nortons-point-trolley-brooklyn/}}</ref>。通過斯提威爾大道及西15街的街車坡度也在這個時候拆除<ref name="Coney Island History Project 2009">{{cite web|url=http://www.coneyislandhistory.org/ask-mr-coney/nortons-point-trolley-ramp|title=The Norton's Point Trolley Ramp|date=2009-05-04|website=Coney Island History Project|accessdate=2016-08-16|archive-date=2020-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926110731/https://www.coneyislandhistory.org/ask-mr-coney/nortons-point-trolley-ramp}}</ref>。

1954年出現了一些問題。[[獨立地鐵系統|獨立地鐵系統]]（IND）開始在卡爾弗線營運[[紐約地鐵D線|D線]]列車<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1954/10/18/archives/bronx-to-coney-ride-in-new-subway-link.html|title=BRONX TO CONEY RIDE IN NEW SUBWAY LINK|last=|first=|date=1954-10-18|work=|newspaper=The New York Times|issn=0362-4331|access-date=2016-08-16|via=|archive-date=2022-03-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220313211953/https://www.nytimes.com/1954/10/18/archives/bronx-to-coney-ride-in-new-subway-link.html}}</ref>。當時軌道以字母命名（即東至西依次為A軌道、B軌道直至H軌道）。然而，IND同時以字母作為路線編號（即[[紐約地鐵A線|A線]]、[[紐約地鐵B線|B線]]直至[[洛克威公園接駁線|H線]]）<ref name=":11">{{Cite web|url=http://thethirdrail.net./0305/stillwell5.html|title=The New BMT Coney Island Terminal|last=Matus|first=Paul|date=May 2003|website=thethirdrail.net|publisher=|page=5|access-date=2016-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310121155/http://thethirdrail.net/0305/stillwell5.html|archive-date=2016-03-10|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。BMT使用數字編號路線，因此問題不大。然而D線行走卡爾弗線，自E和F軌道開出。為免混淆，軌道改為數字編號，直至現在<ref name=":11" />。

1956年，康尼島居民抗議在人魚大道轉乘巴士（現時{{link-en|布魯克林巴士路線列表|List of bus routes in Brooklyn|B74}}線巴士往海門）需要收費，有指15美仙的轉乘費應該廢除，理由時巴士基本上就是車站的附屬<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1956/04/23/archives/coney-bus-fare-protested.html|title=Coney Bus Fare Protested|last=|first=|date=1956-04-23|work=|newspaper=The New York Times|issn=0362-4331|access-date=2016-08-16|via=|archive-date=2019-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190923092040/https://www.nytimes.com/1956/04/23/archives/coney-bus-fare-protested.html}}</ref>。1979年，城市規劃委員會提出了類似建議，康尼島居民將可免費轉乘地鐵和B36/B74線巴士<ref name=":2" />。值得注意的是，此站是唯一沒有在對應的地鐵轉乘終止後得到免費巴士轉乘的車站（與[[BMT卡爾弗線|BMT卡爾弗線]]、[[BMT默特爾大道線|BMT默特爾大道線]]和{{link-en|IRT第三大道線|IRT Third Avenue Line}}形成強烈對比。這些路線停駛後都有巴士轉乘取代）免費轉乘將容許鄰近的2億美元公寓複合有更多人居住，並有政府資助。同時將[[紐約市教育局|馬克·吐溫初級中學]]多樣化並吸引穩定的中產階層<ref name=":2">''The Bulletin'', New York Division Electric Railroaders' Association, January 1987, page 5.</ref>。

1965年康尼島總站安裝了列車離站時間的編配的顯示牌<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://timesmachine.nytimes.com/timesmachine/1965/04/14/issue.html|title=Subway Cars Here To Get Strip Maps Showing One Route; New Series of Maps, Signs and Schedules Are Designed to Take the Guesswork Out of Subway Travel|last=Perlmutter|first=Emanuel|date=1965-04-14|work=|newspaper=The New York Times|issn=0362-4331|access-date=2016-08-16|via=}}</ref>。

=== 車站翻新 ===
[[File:Departure_Board.JPG|thumb]]
車站曾經是一個大樞紐，但康尼島總站自1960年代起每況愈下<ref name=":4" />。到了1980年，整個系統都進入了無維護狀態，總站也不例外。原初預定當年重建。根據《[[紐約每日新聞|紐約每日新聞]]》，翻新的車站將會有「一個亮麗、新輕快的外觀」，同時也是系統內首次安裝連續[[鐵路軌道|焊接軌道]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.nycsubway.org/wiki/The_New_York_Transit_Authority_in_the_1970s#The_Diamond_Jubilee_Brings_Optimism|title=The Diamond Jubilee Brings Optimism|last=|first=|date=|website=www.nycsubway.org|publisher=|access-date=2016-08-15|archive-date=2020-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129032408/https://www.nycsubway.org/wiki/The_New_York_Transit_Authority_in_the_1970s#The_Diamond_Jubilee_Brings_Optimism|dead-url=no}}</ref>。車站的鋼和混凝土受鹽水和維護不當影響嚴重腐蝕<ref name=":1"/>。

1990年代，[[大都會運輸署|大都會運輸署]]（MTA）敲定車站徹底翻新的計劃<ref name=":13">{{Cite web|url=http://thethirdrail.net./0305/stillwell6.html|title=The New BMT Coney Island Terminal|last=Matus|first=Paul|date=May 2003|website=thethirdrail.net|publisher=|page=6|access-date=2016-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161017051059/http://thethirdrail.net/0305/stillwell6.html|archive-date=2016-10-17|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。1999年，MTA要求聯邦資助1.25億美元進行翻新。作為翻新的一部分，車站還計劃了一組{{link-en|衛星碟|satellite dish}}<ref name=":17">{{Cite web|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/archives/boroughs/spruceup-stillwell-125m-plan-coney-terminal-article-1.831734|title=SPRUCEUP FOR STILLWELL – 125M PLAN FOR CONEY TERMINAL|last=Liff|first=Bob|date=1999-06-08|website=nydailynews.com|publisher=[[New_York_Daily_News|New York Daily News]]|access-date=2016-08-16|archive-date=2017-09-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170903163208/http://www.nydailynews.com/archives/boroughs/spruceup-stillwell-125m-plan-coney-terminal-article-1.831734}}</ref>。至此，{{link-en|紐約市交通警察|New York City Transit Police}}在車站鄰近營運一座帳幕，是車站內[[旋轉木馬|旋轉木馬]]的遺蹟<ref name=":17" />。

翻新工程在2001年11月展開<ref name=":1" /><ref name=":13"/>。此段期間，康尼島總站進行了耗資3.1億美元的全面重建<ref name=":14" />，興建期間西城[[紐約地鐵W線|W線]]列車依次維持一個月台開放<ref name="Bahrampour 2002" />。作為翻新工程的一部分，原初的BMT車站大樓正面進行重設，新屋頂安裝了[[光伏模組|太陽能板]]<ref name=":14" />。新總站在2004年5月23日開放，[[紐約地鐵F線|F線]]和[[紐約地鐵Q線|Q線]]列車服務恢復，W線列車服務移到1號和2號軌道<ref name="mta.info facts">{{cite web | title=New York City Transit — History and Chronology | website=mta.info | url=http://web.mta.info/nyct/facts/ffhist.htm | accessdate=2016-08-15 | quote=The newly renovated Stillwell Avenue Terminal reopens and train service returns to Coney Island after a 21-month hiatus during construction | archive-date=2014-01-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140108233754/http://www.mta.info/nyct/facts/ffhist.htm | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=":1" />。整個計劃在2005年5月29日完成，[[紐約地鐵N線|N線]]全面恢復服務<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.mta.info/nyct/service/n_to_coneyisland.htm |title=Noteworthy – N restored to Coney Island |date=2005-05-07 |access-date=2016-09-18  |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20050507105016/http://www.mta.info/nyct/service/n_to_coneyisland.htm |archivedate=2005-05-07  }}</ref>，而行走西城線的W線由D線取代，全部八條軌道都開始營運<ref name=":1">{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2005/05/28/nyregion/and-now-for-the-good-news-from-the-subway-system.html|title=And Now for the Good News From the Subway System|last=Chan|first=Sewell|date=2005-05-28|newspaper=The New York Times|issn=0362-4331|access-date=2016-08-15|archive-date=2022-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220616104426/https://www.nytimes.com/2005/05/28/nyregion/and-now-for-the-good-news-from-the-subway-system.html}}</ref>。工期加速至42個月，同時西城線在興建期間維持有限度服務，以儘量減少鄰近社區的影響<ref name=":14" />。

2010年5月，車站每個月台均設有四部新的電子32英吋列車出發顯示屏。這些顯示屏由調度員根據地鐵時間表的出發時間控制<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://secondavenuesagas.com/2010/06/02/at-coney-island-a-new-sign-for-the-next-train/|title=At Coney Island, a new sign for the next train|last=Kabak|first=Benjamin|date=2010-06-02|website=secondavenuesagas.com|publisher=Second Avenue Sagas|access-date=2016-08-15|archive-date=2019-09-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190918230619/http://secondavenuesagas.com/2010/06/02/at-coney-island-a-new-sign-for-the-next-train/}}</ref>。

2012年[[颶風桑迪|颶風桑迪]]吹襲後，站房嚴重水浸，部分電子儀器受破壞<ref name=":14" />。

